**Question:**  
Examine the following code snippet and identify any code smells. Refactor the code to address these issues:

```java
class BankAccount {
  private double balance;

  public double getBalance() {
    return balance;
  }
  public void setBalance(double balance) {
    this.balance = balance;
  }
}

BankAccount account = new BankAccount();
